description.en:
The Dogefather EcoSystem, created on 29 April 2021, is a decentralized application ecosystem powered by a DeFi (frictionless yield generation) token built on the Ethereum network.

The $DGFTHR token is deflationary, with each transaction having a tax of 2% that is redistributed amongst the holders. The popular redistribution approach incentivizes every investor to HODL and generates tokens in return. The max total supply is 100 quadrillion $DGFTHR, of which 49.7487% was burned to a dead address.

The Dogefather EcoSystem is the native utility token that is used inside of our ecosystem that consists of:

- Decentralized Exchange (DEX)
- NFT Generator Platform
- NFT Marketplace
- Decentralized Autonomous Organization (DAO)
- Dogefather Tap & Dogefather Falcon, first of their kind uniquely developed games for a token on Telegram
